lead_paragraph: Connor Lammert had 15 points, including a clutch 3-pointer in the final minute, and Texas won for the sixth time in its last seven games, beating No. 15 Baylor 67-59 on Monday night.

headline.print_headline: Texas Upsets No. 15 Baylor 67-59 for 6th Win in 7 Games
